<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>والبيهقي في "الشعب<span class="c1">" <span class="c2">(١١٥٨)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
